race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi Mdn Plate
race.comment: EXTRAGALACTIC (7) just missed at Echuca on debut when expected to need it. There was a stack of merit in the effort and she's sure to have come on. Will have to do it the hard way again, but can win if things go to plan, BILLIE (6) peaks off a Moe placing and things could have gone better. She's likely to race more forward and can make the finish again. MOON GODDESS (10) just missed at a short quote at Swan Hill and has more to give. She's quick enough to clear the awkward barrier. The speedy UNA GENTLE (12) resumes and will use the inside barrier to advantage. She's right up to this if presented forward. IMMORTAL TRUTH (9) debuts for a leading metro yard and placed the latest of five jumpouts. Maps well and the betting will be key.
